\rem \q1 Thy name shall be called no more Jacob, but Israel: for as a prince hast thou power with God and with men, and hast prevailed.
\ip 22. Compare verse 51 with Gen. 28. 12 and Heb. 1. 14. —\rem [it]  Christ is the ladder of communication between heaven and earth, between earth and heaven; and angels were messengers and servants to Jacob of old and to Christ upon earth, and are " ministering spirits " " to the heirs of salvation " now.\rem [it]*
