\ip 8. What confirmation of the inspiration of the Pentateuch is there in verse 46?—\rem [it] Jesus quoting it as written of himself.\rem [it]*
\ip 9. What is the abiding testimony against the Jews' unbelief?—\rem [it] The writings of Moses and the prophets, which testify of Christ.\rem [it]*
